title: Jimmy Buffett Brings Margaritaville to Manhattan
itunes:title: Jimmy Buffett Brings Margaritaville to Manhattan
description:
Singer-songwriter Jimmy Buffett and Margaritaville Enterprises CEO John Cohlan discuss opening their $370 million Margaritaville resort in Times Square.

Hosts: Carol Massar and Tim Stenovec. Producer: Paul Brennan.
